                      <h3 style="font-family:'Lucida Grande','Trebuchet MS',Arial;font-size:13pt;font-weight:bold;color:#008C7B;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0">What is Clicktate?</h3>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
                        Clicktate is a <b>revolutionary medical documentation system</b> that is unlike anything you've ever seen. 
                        Web-based, HIPAA and HI-TECH compliant, Clicktate offers EHR functionality at a fraction of the cost of most software, while being incredibly <b>easy to use.</b>
                      </p>
                      <h3 style="font-family:'Lucida Grande','Trebuchet MS',Arial;font-size:13pt;font-weight:bold;color:#008C7B;margin-top:1.5em;margin-bottom:0">State-of-the-Art Note Builder</h3>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
                        Clicktate builds your documents in <b>paragraph form</b> on-the-fly, while interacting with patients. 
                        Data entry is <b>amazingly intuitive</b>, and your completed notes will be organized and legible.
                      </p>
                      <center>                   
                        <IMG style="border:1px solid #c0c0c0;" SRC="http://www.clicktate.com/email/img/ss-console3.png" BORDER="0" title="Screen Shot: Note Builder" alt="Screen Shot: Note Builder" height="318" width="423">
                      </center>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
                        With over 2,000 templates in our ever-expanding library, you'll find templates for most patient problems that you encounter. 
                        And our physician-designed templates use real-world defaults for every option to keep your <b>clicks to a minimum</b>.
                      </p>
                      <h3 style="font-family:'Lucida Grande','Trebuchet MS',Arial;font-size:13pt;font-weight:bold;color:#008C7B;margin-top:1.5em;margin-bottom:0">Efficiently Manage Patient Data</h3>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
                        Clicktate provides seamless integration between the documentation you create and patient data management.
                        Health data (e.g. allergies, medications, diagnoses, vitals) flows automatically between patient documentation and the facesheet,
                        where the patient's health record is organized and at your fingertips.                       
                      </p>
                      <center>                   
                        <IMG SRC="http://www.clicktate.com/email/img/ss-facesheet.png" BORDER="0" title="Screen Shot: Facesheet" alt="Screen Shot: Facesheet" height="642" width="540">
                      </center>
                      <h3 style="font-family:'Lucida Grande','Trebuchet MS',Arial;font-size:13pt;font-weight:bold;color:#008C7B;margin-top:1.5em;margin-bottom:0">Always Available and Secure</h3>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
                        As a web-based system, your Clicktate documentation and patient information is easily retrievable when you need it, where you need it: in the office, an exam room, or anywhere with Internet access.
                        We use SSL 256-bit encryption to ensure the safety and security of your medical data, and are HIPAA and HI-TECH compliant to protect your patients and yourself. 
                      </p>                   
                      <h3 style="font-family:'Lucida Grande','Trebuchet MS',Arial;font-size:13pt;font-weight:bold;color:#008C7B;margin-top:1.5em;margin-bottom:0">Affordable</h3>
                      <p style="margin-top:0.6em;margin-bottom:0.7em;">
